  • XBridgeBasePlugin

    This is the basic Plugin class , you should inherit it , and implement a sub class eg. if js call an plugin like this: window.XWebView.callNative(‘TestPlugin’,‘testAction’, {“a”:12,“c”:“d”}, ‘callbackName’, ‘xxxyyyzzz’); you should implement an class TestPlugin that inherit XBridgeBasePlugin and implement method

    • (BOOL)excute:(NSString *)action params:(NSDictionary *)params callback:(XBridgeCallBack *)jsBridgeCallback; then you can get params like this actiontestAction params {“a”:12,“c”:“d”} finally do your job
